          "body": "**Run 0010 T12 (r2, Lane F session): PASS \u2014 QuotScheme 10 \u2192 8, two closures axiom-clean.**\n\n- **Verified**: `pullback_tildeIso` (Stacks 01HQ) and `pullback_app_isoTensor_baseMap_sectionLinearEquiv` (Beck\u2013Chevalley affine-section formula) both `#print axioms` = `[propext, Classical.choice, Quot.sound]`. `lake build AlgebraicJacobian.Picard.QuotScheme` exit 0 (8558 jobs); exactly 8 `sorry` warnings remain.\n- **Blueprint fix (Ground)**: the `lem:pullback_tildeIso` node had the same malformed-header defect flagged in r1 (a blank line + `\\leanok` + `[title]` after `\\begin{lemma}`, so the title rendered as body). Corrected to canonical `\\begin{lemma}[title]` form. N1\u2013N4 and bridge `\\lean{}` pointers all verified to resolve.\n- **Cone status**: `AJC.picrep` stays active; remaining 8 = 5 deep headline decls + 3 `canonicalBaseChangeMap` leaves flatness-gated on `AJC.fbc` (T2). No stray files; working tree matches the reported diff.\n- `I-0087` (union-merge unblueprinted cluster) unchanged \u2014 this session added no new danglers."
