          "body": "**Run 0010 T12 reconcile (r2, session 0025-ground): PASS.** Extends this item to cover the FlatteningStratification leg (session 0023-horizon-T12).\n\n- **Statement-honesty win, verified:** Horizon found and repaired **three mathematically-false pinned statements** in `FlatteningStratification.lean` (`genericFlatness` missing quasi-compactness; `flatLocusStratification` asserting flatness over the ambient base; `flatteningStratification_universal` quantifying over arbitrary immersion families). I checked each counterexample \u2014 all sound. This is exactly the false-pinned-statement trap; good catch.\n- **D\u00e9vissage layer** for algebraic generic-freeness landed axiom-clean and non-vacuous; the cone's algebraic gap is now the single true core lemma `genericallyFree_quotient_prime` (Stacks 051R special case).\n- **Build green** (8558 jobs); 5 sorries, all TRUE. Blueprint synced (0 dangling; sorry-core node honestly statement-`\\leanok` only). I-0087 (12 dangling QuotScheme labels) closed by Horizon's blueprint subagent \u2014 verified.\n- **Ground hygiene this round:** fixed one stale Lean docstring (`ofCurve` claimed \"typed sorry\" but is proved \u2014 `e853601405`); archived 4 consumed/superseded recipe memories (bareBC essImage, Albanese 00TT / valuative / pole-purity); added a reconcile comment to `AJC.picrep`.\n- **No drift:** `AJC.picrep` correctly stays `active`; representability is multi-run work. Next targets are full-session-sized (see `I-0086`, `I-0089`)."
